Nothing and NO ONE is ever worth closing your heart over ❤️ -  It’s your birthright to know that divine energy is always available to you. It’s within you. It can’t get through you if you close your heart. -  Decide to stay open. Choose NOT to close, even though closing your heart may feel instinctual. -  Closing your heart does NOT protect you from anything, it just limits your experiences. -  Do not let anything that happens in your life be important enough to close. -  Stay open and eventually so much energy will come through you that it will flow out from you. -  Relax and release and stay open. -  There is nothing and NO ONE worth closing over….. Ever! - ❤️❤️❤️

On mindset, positivity and self compassion
❤️
You’re doing the work to change your old beliefs to new empowering ones
❤️
You’re being positive in your speech, attitude and chosen perspective as much as possible
❤️
And still you have your moments of trigger, feelings of defeat, doubt that all your hard work is working. It’s working!!!
❤️
The effects of this self awareness work will show up for you. Sometimes in small very subtle ways and in moments the impact will feel massive and sometimes it won’t seem that way at all
❤️
One key element I believe we forget to include is self compassion. With all your amazing effort to grow and evolve please include self compassion.
You’re never going to be a perfectly refined human.
❤️
I welcome you… me… all of us on the conscious path of growth to go easy in those moments that feel like old “negative feelings” ❤️
Sometimes the best thing we can do is simply admit the way we feel and accept it for the moment and know that your path to internal emotional freedom is not broken cause you have an experience of feeling like the “old you”
❤️
Try the tone you’d take with a sweet, innocent child with yourself in those moments.
Easy does it. You’ve got this. Love yourself.
❤️
Then sit in awe at the beauty, vastness, depth and rawness of who you are.
❤️
You’re perfect as you are… right bere, right now.

Music is my f’n answer 
💯
To whoever needs to hear this message…
❤️
Remind yourself that anything is possible
🎶
Pursue what you love
🎧
Don’t let age, opinions of others, social norms, doubt, complacency, “logic” get in the way of pursuing what you love
🪐
The universe wants for you what you want for yourself
👊🏻
Have integrity. Take action to be good at what you want and bring your best energy to the world
🙏
You deserve to be happy and live the life you desire
😽
Thank you for all the support. Thank you God.
